<p>Dear <%= @client.name %>,</p>

<p>Your task "<strong><%= @task.title %></strong>" has been marked as completed by <%= @freelancer.name %>.</p>

<p>Here are the details:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Description:</strong> <%= @task.description %></li>
  <li><strong>Budget:</strong> <%= @task.budget %> ZMK</li>
  <li><strong>Deadline:</strong> <%= @task.deadline.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></li>
  <li><strong>Status:</strong> <%= @task.status.capitalize %></li>
</ul>

<p>You can review the completed work and provide a review.</p>

<p>Thank you for using Gighive!</p>